par0\qj{section 2.32}}}{ shall disclose to the appointing authority for that board, committee, commission, or council if the member has filed subsequent to senate confirmation a registration statement pursuant to the federal }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Foreign Agents Registration Act of 1938}}}{, as amended, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{22 U.S.C. \'a7611 et seq.}}}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2018 Acts, ch 1061, \'a72}}}\par}}